title: kathy ireland Office By Bush Furniture Safety Features
description:
All pieces of furniture from kathy ireland Office by Bush Furniture are built with safety as a top priority. Rounded corners, soft close hinges, tempered safety glass, and the Bush StabiliBar TV Safety Brace come together to give you peace of mind.
